2004-07-25	danp_typo
	* cvsroot/typo3xdev/tx_ttnews/Attic/ext_typoscript_setup.txt 1.11:
	* cvsroot/typo3xdev/tx_ttnews/pi/class.tx_ttnews.php 1.25:
