2004-07-20	rupertgermann
	* cvsroot/typo3xdev/tx_ttnews/Attic/ext_typoscript_constants.txt 1.3:
	* cvsroot/typo3xdev/tx_ttnews/Attic/ext_typoscript_setup.txt 1.7:
